Asian Delite, located off Bloomfield Avenue in West Caldwell, NJ, offers large portions of tasty, fresh Chinese and Japanese favorites at a reasonable price. The ambience isn't exceptional -- it is located in a New Jersey strip mall, after all -- but the food is freshly prepared and served quickly in large portions by attentive waitstaff.  The menu (asiandelite.com/asiandel…) covers most of your expected Chinese and Japanese favorites.  Most dinner entrees range in price from $10 to $20; lunch specials are offered until 3pm.
